# This directory holds the UniFFI-generated Swift surface for the Rust core.
#
# The real file, RustyNESCore.swift, is BUILD-GENERATED by
# scripts/build-ios-xcframework.sh (UniFFI 0.31 library-mode codegen from
# librustynes_ios.a) and is gitignored — it is regenerated on every build, never
# hand-edited. This .gitkeep keeps the directory present so the XcodeGen spec's
# `Generated` source group resolves before the first generation.
